{
  "stem": "2391.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because that was a problem too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't just go wherever you wanted, you know, and, and be accepted.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They'll get papers to stay, and they get ration cards.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, because that was part of it too, to get-- to get food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here we were, and we got our papers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But these were still papers with the name Cohn.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So later-- you know, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The mayor of our village gave us papers with a fake name, in case we got checked out in the street.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they wouldn't arrest us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you lived-- so now you met up with your father in Macon?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Macon, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he lived in a little motel somewhere.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like two small rooms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we-- we lived there for quite awhile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was not very fancy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe-- we came there in spring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Till fall.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, late fall.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe five, six months.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No occupation.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You didn't see any German uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the government was collaborating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called it a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were collaborating with Germany, and they did everything they asked them to do.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the police worked for the-- you know, for the pro-German French government, which was the Vichy government.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's another-- that's another funny story, which sounds like-- you know, very unusual.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After my father had left the camp, he was in Toulouse, all the way in the south, for a few days.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he walked the street, and here he sees somebody knows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says, Charles, what are you doing?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it turns out he sees a French officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was during the last days of the French-- before they were, they were taken over.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was still wearing his uniform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was his first cousin.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
